com.ibm.team.process.common.advice
Interface IReportInfoCollector

All Known Subinterfaces:
IAdvisorInfoCollector, IParticipantInfoCollector
public interface IReportInfoCollector

Collector which is passed to implementors of operation advisors and participants. Advisors and participants add infos to the collector as they perform their processing.

Since:
0.5
See Also:
IAdvisorInfoCollector, IParticipantInfoCollector
